自此之後一定要係咁打喊路整通佢先安落</blockquote><br />\n我係連通都痛，雙手禁鼻噴氣，仲痛過本身，游水1.6池都潛唔到底，一浸低小小就勁大壓力，同我細個有中耳炎有關係？</blockquote><br />\n冇關係<br />\n你試下用入耳式耳筒聽住歌 同一路食香口膠 <br />\n你身體對氣壓變化比較敏感</blockquote><br />\n上一次就係咁，去台灣第一次唔知會痛，結果忍左成程，之後台灣回程上網check左，我狂食香口膠，睇電影最大聲，<br />\n<br />\n最後好左7成，但landing時都仲有D痛，雖然係好過第一次好多</blockquote><br />\n同我一樣又係第一次搭飛機去台灣 最尾個幾個字機程痛到生不如死 就算打喊路吞口水feel到耳通左一樣咁痛 回程個時係咁食香口膠 得左"},{"pid":"fe9a2ac0a2d92ed4f772a05e1a286c31023f52c2","tid":466280,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T18:35:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上個禮拜喺西班牙飛德國都係咁 飛到中途右耳好似聾咗咁 嚇到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩landing打左個喊露就通返<br />\n平時都未試過會咁 就算搭十幾個鐘飛機都唔怕 唔知關唔關成晚冇訓事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睡眠不捉有感冒都會令唔知咩收窄 大啲機會痛"},{"pid":"6ee990485122ffad5bbed2f0711cafdbb37383f3","tid":466280,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T18:35:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上個禮拜喺西班牙飛德國都係咁 飛到中途右耳好似聾咗咁 嚇到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩landing打左個喊露就通返<br />\n平時都未試過會咁 就算搭十幾個鐘飛機都唔怕 唔知關唔關成晚冇訓事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睡眠不足有感冒都會令唔知咩收窄 大啲機會痛</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d03e249256875cb9131e963e19dd92170de0f45a","tid":466280,"uid":13689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T18:41:30.000Z","msg":"應該係耳壓問題，之前都試過係咁<br />\n真係痛到天冷都出曬汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後買左對專for搭飛機用嘅耳塞(中間有filter)就好啲，最多都係耳塞但就冇痛<br />\n戴左之後聽到人講野不過就細聲啲"},{"pid":"4f7ab89bfdf4b43899c677b18add80904c20d251","tid":466280,"uid":98624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T18:43:06.000Z","msg":"鼻塞搭飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頭痛到想死<br />\n平衡耳壓都無用"},{"pid":"5708d9959e08ca1fea1ff759ada3b267dfaa2125","tid":466280,"uid":35557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T18:47:14.000Z","msg":"人生第一次搭飛機<br />\n起飛同降機痛到pk<br />\n本身我隻耳仔有問題<br />\n痛到頭到爆<br />\n落機之後第二日先通返"},{"pid":"06c7e8202965472393d32b3810ba23412e71f2d7","tid":466280,"uid":17420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T18:47:25.000Z","msg":"我都係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  得打喊路先有用<br />\n但係唔眼訓果陣真係痛成程<br />\n有冇方法易D打喊路"},{"pid":"19ce50c0a7a3e22765a53f634ce8fd20d5d41d2d","tid":466280,"uid":141496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T18:48:37.000Z","msg":"我落左機之類 吞口水就通返"},{"pid":"8aac99608c9f162bc1c52e84146767c931ae09d5","tid":466280,"uid":75404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T18:53:03.000Z","msg":"上次去日本 眼眉位痛到癡線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb9493fd1f5c78654fea9e77533df4245c39001c","tid":466280,"uid":97756,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T18:53:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>氣壓問題，潛水都會咁<br />\n用手鏈住個鼻，閉口用鼻呼氣，就會通返耳仔。<br />\n勁既唔鏈都做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌！我一直以為得自己知到可以咁做！我又唔知點同人地形容呢樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81da1de4498650b583bc7d3e0738fb83708b4364","tid":466280,"uid":10586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T19:01:30.000Z","msg":"落到地通翻果下係最爽不過痛到仆街"},{"pid":"c1f72b61b1afb4af28c5bd5433b65580a5b713e0","tid":466280,"uid":73849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T19:12:53.000Z","msg":"最近臨飛之前傷風鼻塞，起飛嗰下都仲ok，降落痛撚到仆街仲要持續咗兩日都係咁，去睇耳鼻喉科先知兩隻耳仔入面都出咗血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望樓主唔會搞到要睇專科咁大劑"},{"pid":"492f4cb2843f2bb5c1cc6624624431101069fba0","tid":466280,"uid":99055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T19:26:44.000Z","msg":"之前撘過幾次飛機都無乜事 吞下口水或者禁住個鼻呼氣就無事 但係最近一次痛到上太陽穴果個位 個腦好似就爆咁 做乜都無用 真係痛到想即刻落機 最後逼自己訓先無事"},{"pid":"d5d6b8a868aab37abef6498e7ce3f339104efe48","tid":466280,"uid":5182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T19:31:00.000Z","msg":"我次次去程都無事,係回程返香港先出事,唔知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea2be51b27df4e2f57f69c9021ddacc63fcb0c9","tid":466280,"uid":76542,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T19:31:10.000Z","msg":"耳罩 口罩 眼罩"},{"pid":"07e1fec66fb77120ebc36c0856c46cec4882d59b","tid":466280,"uid":32623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T19:40:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都會<br />\n但淨係得搭日本嗰陣先會<br />\n搭泰國,大陸都唔會痛<br />\n有冇人明點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我上次去日本都爆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d4a9eef9f2da2582a7821ca1ea7661ebc99487","tid":466280,"uid":58527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T19:54:27.000Z","msg":"未進化既人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未適應到現今科技既驅體<br />\n同暈車浪，暈船浪既人一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441fa91f87fb5b5796942f678cd2c7a8ebf085de","tid":466280,"uid":11862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T20:06:16.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以好似我咁唔洗閉氣唔洗捏鼻都通到耳仔？<br />\n耳仔用一用力會有滴一聲，跟住就通左<br />\n如果hold住道力抖氣 就會聽到捂住耳仔個d抖氣聲<br />\n<br />\n利申：搭幾耐飛機都唔會耳仔唔舒服"},{"pid":"aabeafa944fae043c2ccbe68cb20f5ebf0ba0f7e","tid":466280,"uid":41791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T20:15:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人可以好似我咁唔洗閉氣唔洗捏鼻都通到耳仔？<br />\n耳仔用一用力會有滴一聲，跟住就通左<br />\n如果hold住道力抖氣 就會聽到捂住耳仔個d抖氣聲<br />\n<br />\n利申：搭幾耐飛機都唔會耳仔唔舒服</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廢嘅人先要捏住。<br />\n我冇呢個問題<br />\n但我有另一個問題就係<br />\n<br />\n搭親廉航就land個陣個腦好似要爆咁。<br />\n香港去日本<br />\n英國去德國<br />\n但長途一定冇事"},{"pid":"fc589e6c10ce7ac8f9dfd86b9940eb23cfbf87dc","tid":466280,"uid":10775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T20:31:25.000Z","msg":"我身邊朋友都無呢個問題一直以為自己有事 原來咁多人一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人飛到一半果陣唔單止耳仔痛 係個頭同隻眼痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  上次日本返香港痛左成粒幾鐘 <br />\nFeel到部飛機下降左些許高度先無再痛"},{"pid":"0639891a0e4f1715108985f7e00eb5459495833c","tid":466280,"uid":102300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T20:34:49.000Z","msg":"係咪個鼻塞住上機呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89e64a5be9e047d9695df0c8b88dda6ad5152ee","tid":466280,"uid":3995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T21:40:03.000Z","msg":"有無人係單邊耳會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我用手㩒住鼻噴氣嗰種方法降壓，右耳無事但左耳無乜效，試過幾次都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de8e98f65cc48ad662e72dab0986e8e8bb2f89bb","tid":466280,"uid":27954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T21:53:33.000Z","msg":"耳水極度不平衡"}]}